lish</a> | \n  <a href=\"README_zh.md\">中文</a>\n</div>\n\n## 概述\n\nAKShare One MCP Server 是一个用于管理和提供金融数据的服务器。它基于 AKShare 数据库构建，可以方便地获取和处理各种金融数据。\n\n## 安装\n\n要安装 AKShare One MCP Server，请按照以下步骤操作：\n\n1. 克隆仓库：\n   bash\n   git clone https://github.com/your-repo/akshare-one-mcp-server.git\n   \n\n2. 进入项目目录：\n   bash\n   cd akshare-one-mcp-server\n   \n\n3. 安装依赖项：\n   bash\n   pip install -r requirements.txt\n   \n\n## 配置\n\n在启动服务器之前，需要进行一些配置。请编辑 `config.json` 文件以设置数据库连接和其他相关参数。\n\n示例 `config.json` 文件：\njson\n{\n  \"database\": {\n    \"host\": \"localhost\",\n    \"port\": 27017,\n    \"name\": \"akshare\"\n  },\n  \"server\": {\n    \"host\": \"0.0.0.0\",\n    \"port\": 8000\n  }\n}\n\n\n## 启动服务器\n\n完成配置后，可以通过以下命令启动服务器：\nbash\npython main.py\n\n\n## API 文档\n\nAKShare One MCP Server 提供了丰富的 API 接口来获取和处理金融数据。详细的 API 文档可以在 [这里](API_DOCS_URL) 查看。\n\n## 贡献\n\n欢迎贡献代码！如果您有任何改进或新功能的想法，请提交 Pull Request 或 Issue。\n\n## 许可证\n\n本项目采用 MIT 许可证。详细信息请参见 [LICENSE](LICENSE) 文件。","category":"filesystem","tags":["金融数据服务","MongoDB","RESTful API","AKShare","量化基础设施"],"version":"0.0.0","npmPackage":"yuping322-stock-akshare11","securityScore":59,"requiresApiKey":false,"platforms":["linux","macos","windows"],"isOfficial":false,"isNew":false,"toolCount":0,"installStatus":"not_installed","installable":false,"installMethod":"none","sourceUrl":"https://github.com/zwldarren/akshare-one-mcp","source":"modelscope","configHint":"MongoDB需独立部署；推荐使用Docker快速启动","envSchema":{},"envRequired":[],"isVerified":false,"isHosted":false,"capabilities":["量化投研平台","金融数据中台","AI投顾数据底座"]},{"serverId":"@akuity-argocd-mcp","friendlyName":"Argo CD MCP控制器","friendlyNameEn":"akuity","description":"将Kubernetes GitOps平台Argo CD能力通过MCP协议暴露，实现AI驱动的声明式应用部署与状态同步。","descriptionEn":"","category":"other","tags":["GitOps","Argo CD","Kubernetes","MCP控制器","DevOps自动化"],"version":"0.0.0","npmPackage":"argocd-mcp@latest","securityScore":59,"requiresApiKey":false,"platforms":["linux","macos","windows"],"isOfficial":false,"isNew":false,"toolCoun